int offsetRecords

The cursor position.

An internal counter of the position of the stream. If the stream has more pages this will be incremented with each nextPage().

Definition at line 30 of file EaglePageProviderStream.h.

int totalRecords

The total amount of records.

You should never access this directly since its value may be virtual or invalid - instead use EaglePageProvider_pagesRemaining()
